$interpreted: Simon: Darn it, where did everyone else go? It has been a while yet not a single person has shown up to help!
Hestia: Have a taste of this!
Hestia: Done and~ done!
Karnulla: Have you taken care of him?
Hestia: Hehe, it was a piece of cake~
Karnulla: Looks like you did indeed take care of him...
Hestia: Yep. I'll leave him in your hands. I'm going to release these Platypuses.
Hestia: HEY! Didn't you say that you wouldn't attack me?
Karnulla: My exact words were "before we take down the humans..." Now that this human is defeated, the promise automatically expires as well!
Hestia: Wha...don't you have any shame!?
Karnulla: As long as you are gone, those Platypuses that are sitting in my home right now will be ours to enjoy!
Hestia: Look out! Behind you!
Karnulla: Hmph, you really think I will fall for a cliché like that?
Simon: You lowly creatures...need to at least get one no matter what...
Karnulla: Let go of him, now!
Hestia: Eat this!
Simon: WAAH!!
Simon: Oww! That hurt! Damnit...I'll get you for this someday!
Dark Colored Frogodile: Gagaga!
Karnulla: Haha, good to see that you're safe.
Hestia: So, what now? You still want to fight?
Karnulla: ......
Karnulla: Didn't expect that damn human to be so lively after that beating. I broke my promise because of that...
Hestia: Therefore?
Karnulla: I bet he made a huge mess inside my home. Got to go back and clean things up.
Karnulla: If I come out only to see you and those Platypuses still here, don't blame me from what's going to happen!
Hestia: You're plotting something again, aren't you?
Karnulla: I clean up fast. I advise you to start moving right away!
Hestia: ...Is he displaying a conscience? It can't be...
Hestia: Whatever. Everyone, wake up! We need to go now!
Karnulla: After escaping from a major disaster, treat yourself to a nice sunbath. Relaxes both the mind and the body, doesn't it?
Platypus: Keke~ Ke~
Karnulla: Well, well, now that you experienced relaxation, it's time for you folks to taste fear again~Boys~ Grab them all and bring them back!
Hestia: You bully! I thought you became a good guy.
Hestia: Turns out a bad guy will always be a bad guy. They never ever change!
Karnulla: Hmph, last time, I worked with you only because the situation was desperate. This time, I'm definitely going to have their meat for lunch!
Karnulla: I'm also going to use your fishtail as a toothpick!
Hestia: Over my dead body! Eat this!
